title: Alessandro Cicutti
text:
Alessandro Cicutti (born 26 May 1987 in <a href="Gemona%20del%20Friuli">Gemona del Friuli</a>) is an <a href="Italians">Italian</a> <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> goalkeeper.
He signed in 2011-2012 season for <a href="Vicenza%20Calcio">Vicenza</a>.
